{"schema":"allo-reading-book@1","slug":"56437-akabwa-ka-ammu-akato","title":"Ammu's Puppy","description":"Ammu talina kabwa kato,Naye agamba mikwano gye mbu akalina! Akabwake bakayita Shankar, bwagamba.Shankar ayagala nnyo amenvu bwagamba.Abagamba bingi nyo ku Shankar era nemikwano gye jagala okujja okukasisinkana. Naye kati Ammu anakolaki?","language":"Luganda","langCode":"lg","isRtl":false,"level":"2","orientation":"landscape","authors":["Bulyaba Ruth"],"illustrators":["Soumya Menon"],"originalAuthors":[],"publisher":"AfLIA","license":"CC BY 4.0","licenseUrl":"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/","sourceId":"storyweaver","contentType":"story","source":{"id":"storyweaver","name":"StoryWeaver, Pratham Books","url":"https://storyweaver.org.in/en/stories/56437-akabwa-ka-ammu-akato"},"cover":{"card":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/696665/size3/5c7d534c8828504a66ff3855ce3b80ab.jpg","large":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/696665/size6/5c7d534c8828504a66ff3855ce3b80ab.jpg"},"audio":null,"pages":[{"n":1,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/14462/size6/92ebe5ce770bfa158070e7ebe2fd3381.jpg","text":"Ammu talina kaana ka mbwa kato.\nNaye yagambye buli omu kusomero mbu alin","words":null},{"n":2,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/14463/size6/3ee71c4f2362c572f2fc1dd2395c439c.jpg","text":"\"Akaana kange akembwa bakayita Shankar,\" yagamba Venu","words":null},{"n":3,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/14464/size6/b9c5a6cf803cacf5e0c0df5cd04f0a0a.jpg","text":"Kati Venu, Abdul,Kumari and Unni bagamba Ammu mbu bajja kugenda ewabwe okulaba Shankar. Ammu yanyenya omutwe.\"Tekisoboka, nabagamba.","words":null},{"n":4,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/14465/size6/214cb8c99e0d431534f2d228963ea744.jpg","text":"\"Lwaki?\" nebabuuza.\nKubanga Shankar atya ekibinja kyabantu, Ammu nabadamu.\n\"Kati tujja kuzanya naye omwoomu,\" Kumari nagamba.","words":null},{"n":5,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/14466/size6/67a763d016360b9eabdaa18bc01659d3.jpg","text":"\"Temusobola,\" Ammu nagamba.\n\"Lwaki?\" Unni nabuza","words":null},{"n":6,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/14467/size6/f4ffd5a2a8fa5c707d4ec0444fe6b383.jpg","text":"\"Kati tujja kuja enkya,\" Abdul nagamba.\n\"Tujja kumuleterayo amenvu,\" Venu nagamba","words":null},{"n":7,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/14468/size6/d4170efd879776bc341a682685354a11.jpg","text":"Olwegulo olwo, Ammu yabuza Achan oba anamugulirayo akabwa akato.","words":null},{"n":8,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/14469/size6/891edd0fe3bdb7ff62f65e745cc22101.jpg","text":"Tayagala kulowoza ku lwankya.","words":null},{"n":9,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/14470/size6/d9b10f5bc696bdd46b45ec293748916a.jpg","text":"\"Sigala ewaka leera,\" Amma namugamba.\nEra Ammu nayosa kusomero.","words":null},{"n":10,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/14471/size6/7d0235953e75181628922ce453eace16.jpg","text":"Olwegulo olwo, Venu, Abdul, Kumari and Unni bajja ewaka.\n\"Lwaki tewaze kusomero leero?\" Unni abiza.","words":null},{"n":11,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/14472/size6/510707a87a9fe4e1604b883cf28c766b.jpg","text":"\"Tulabye Shanakar,\" Abdul Nagamba.\n\"Ewa?\" Ammu nabuza.\n\"Mu nnimiro,\" Kamari nagamba.","words":null},{"n":12,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/14473/size6/53124e8ee09c4aa1dfdc67b8ce342289.jpg","text":"\"Abadde tayagala kuzanya kapiira,\" Abdul nagamba.\n Obuzibu, Ammu yasituka mubuliri. Nadduka wabweru.","words":null},{"n":13,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/14474/size6/cb990da3999e8c9c4e4256bcc031fe18.jpg","text":"Kibadde kitufu. Waliyo akabwa akato munimiro.Shankar!\n\"Naye sikaddugavu,\" Venus nagamba. \"Wakitaka.\"","words":null},{"n":14,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/14475/size6/231bf270bf1af43c2f0d15e3101b80e6.jpg","text":"\"Tatya kibinja kyabantu,\" Abdul nagamba.\n\"Oh,\" Ammu nagamba. \"Nakikoze ekyo\"","words":null},{"n":15,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/14476/size6/56a1f239dced11048006f6060aa47cc5.jpg","text":"\"Tayagala kuzanya kapiira,\" Unni nagamba.\n\"Oh,\" Ammu nagamba. \"Nakikoze!\"","words":null},{"n":16,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/14477/size6/4ac7f3ee397248231bcd331f2427c41d.jpg","text":"\"Naye ayagala amenvu,\" Kumari Nagamba.\nNagamba, sikyekyo?\" Ammu nasanyuka.","words":null}],"stats":{"pages":16,"words":169}}